shared.model.map

Class Vertex

  • java.lang.Object
    • shared.model.map.Vertex

  • public final class Vertex
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains a normalized VertexLocation also contains a building object, if there is no building on the vertex, set as null. Also has a port object, if there is no port connected to the vertex, then it is initialized as null.
    Author:
    Joel Bradley
